_text = "I could talk about this backyard for hours. I could talk about the fires we had out back, the stories shared around the hottub, the blanket forts I made outside, to the times falling off the trampoline.\n\nI spent a lot of time outside as a kid. We spent the summers biking around the neighbourhood until we all were old enough to drive cars. However, this backyard always acted like a meet up place for all my friends, even as we grew older.\n\nThis house is filled with memories that even ive forgotten. I sometimes wish I had taken more photos, just to preserve those precious moments. Maybe at the time they just didn't feel as important as they do now."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, BackyardFireTextRoom2, BackyardFireTextRoom2, false)
